1. Download Jenkin and run by  default jenkin runs on port 8080 url:http://localhost:8080/ 

Use the following command at command prompt:
java -jar jenkins.war --httpPort=9090

If you want to use https use the following command:
java -jar jenkins.war --httpsPort=9090  

2. check and add maven and TestNG plugins from Available.

3. Create maven style project.
	3.0 Source Code Management: None
	3.1 In Build: Provide pom.xml file path
	3.2 In Post-build Actions: select TestNG XML report pattern 

click Apply and Save

4. Run/Execute Build and verify the test case result in console.

